text: Isabella van Toorn (born 9 July 1995) is a Dutch water polo player. She was a member of the Netherlands women's national water polo team. She played at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2016 Women's European Water Polo Championship, and 2016 Summer Olympics women's qualification. == References == == Other websites == * Interview Isabella van Toorn na mislopen Olympische Spelen Studio Alphen, March 27, 2016 Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch water polo players
